Name: Rogue Quest: The Vault of the Lost Tyrant
About the game: Cassandra Nech is one of the members in the renowned Rogue's Guild, which gathers adventurers and treasure hunters - the most skilled, the bravest, the most resourceful ever. Armed with her trusty crossbow, Antoinette, Cassandra is trying to recover the legendary Sea Tyrant's treasure, who was a long-time forgotten warlord; an easy task, to one like her. Still, things could be not that easy: it looks like someone else is looking for that treasure. Moreover, something dangerous could be hiding in those ancient caves. Something dark and... terrible! Features A funny, adventurous and original story. Pixel graphic and retro-style gameplay. No pixel hunting. In game hints system.
